-- Obama calls for rollback of Wall St bonuses
-- 
-- Thu Jan 14, 2010 1:22pm EST
-- http://www.reuters.com/article/2010/01/14/us-obama-banks-announcement-idUSTRE60D46J20100114

 

 WASHINGTON  (Reuters) - President Barack Obama on Thursday urged Wall Street to roll back executive bonuses as he proposed a fee to repay taxpayers for a financial bailout, saying "we want our money back and we're going to get it." 

